      youtubeLink="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9CVPPGYaytg"
      title="Rony - The Virtual Friend"
      about="The story of a lonely and dejected boy who finds solace in talking to an imaginary friend that turns out to be his long-suppressed alter ego."
